@startuml
title Echoes of the Hollow Crown - Timeline Puzzle (Truth vs Reveal Order)

' =========================
' TRUE HISTORY (Chronological - What Actually Happened)
' =========================

package "TRUE HISTORY (800 Years)" {

[~800 Years Ago\nQueen Veyra uses Crown\nCataclysm splits world] as Cataclysm

[Seven Echo Shards scatter] as ShardsScatter

[Realm of Stone forms Anchor Wardens\n"One Primary + Tithe" doctrine] as StoneDoctrine

[Realm of Veil forms Rememberers\nForgetting = mercy] as VeilDoctrine

[Shattered Middle forms Shard Cult] as CultBirth

[First forced Hollowing experiments (secret)] as ForcedHollowEarly

[Hollow Order founded\n"Peace through emptiness"] as HollowOrderBirth

[Rift begins widening again] as RiftAwakens

[Story Present\nKael at mother's grave] as Present
}

Cataclysm --> ShardsScatter
ShardsScatter --> StoneDoctrine
StoneDoctrine --> VeilDoctrine
VeilDoctrine --> CultBirth
CultBirth --> ForcedHollowEarly
ForcedHollowEarly --> HollowOrderBirth
HollowOrderBirth --> RiftAwakens
RiftAwakens --> Present

' =========================
' STORY REVEAL ORDER (What Audience Learns)
' =========================

package "STORY REVEAL ORDER" {

[Layer 1: Safe village life\nResonance tithe is holy] as Phase1

[Layer 2: Rules are breaking\nFirst anomalies & dying traveler] as Phase2

[Layer 3: We are not alone\nCross Rift + Veil philosophy] as Phase3

[Layer 4: Bloodline & Shards\nForced Hollowing revealed] as Phase4

[Layer 5: Full Cataclysm truth\nVeyra's echo + seven Shards] as Phase5

[Final: Impossible choice\nReunite or destroy?] as Phase6
}

Phase1 --> Phase2
Phase2 --> Phase3
Phase3 --> Phase4
Phase4 --> Phase5
Phase5 --> Phase6

' =========================
' CONNECTION LINKS (How Reveals Map Back to True History)
' =========================

Phase1 .right.> StoneDoctrine : "Official lie"
Phase2 .right.> RiftAwakens : "Anomalies explained"
Phase3 .right.> VeilDoctrine : "Other survival method"
Phase4 .right.> ForcedHollowEarly : "Dark technique"
Phase5 .right.> Cataclysm : "Origin of everything"
Phase6 .right.> ShardsScatter : "Final puzzle piece"

' =========================
' KEY ECHO (Veyra's Influence)
' =========================

[Veyra's Final Whisper\n"Remember everything... and choose to forget"] as Whisper

Whisper --> Cataclysm
Whisper --> Present : "Echo in the grave (Chapter 1)"

@enduml